reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 3, 2020
reviews.reviewText: I bought this to replace a Laptop I bought 2 years ago that I gave to someone else in the house. Everything is working great, it was easy to set up, runs fast, and the graphics are great. I have watched videos and it has performed wonderfully. I think it is an excellent Laptop, overall, to use at home. I cannot speak for its gaming abilities, but I think av gamer knows what they need. So for us average people, I think this will fill the bill at a good price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2020
reviews.reviewText: I've been a Mac guy for over 30 years, but I must say this is pretty impressive. Laptop dimensions exterior are 16 1/4 x 10 3/4, so fits nicely in Amazon Basics sleeve exterior17 1/4 x 13. And whole thing easily into 18 inch Komal Passion Leather messenger bag. Screen is stunning. Set up remarkably easy including Canon printer, Elements keyboard, Kensington trackball, etc.I only got this because there is a program that is essential for my business that will not run on 64 bit Catalina, so best choice was switch to PC for that application But I am impressed. PC has come a long way. And probably 1/3 the price of comparable Mac.Shipped promptly from this seller.Highly recommended.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 29, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very good deal.
reviews.reviewText: Nice computer up to date and fast. Wish I had something other than Hughes net because this computer operates fast. A real bargain getting it used even though you could not tell that it had ever been used at all.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 16, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Webcam may not give the best image
reviews.reviewText: Good laptop for the money. Only concern was the webcam, not very good picture quality, ended up using an external webcam with wider view and sharper image. The seller offered to replace but would have been too much. Already had a bunch of programs installed and couldn’t afford to be without it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 8, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Really thin and lightweight.
reviews.reviewText: Great laptop! Really thin and lightweight. I. Like the black color, the fast startup and the price was right, for me. Glad I purchased this.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 17, 2020
reviews.reviewText: So far so good. I love this computer it's my baby. It's light weight which I thought would be a problem because I like things with a little heftiness to it, but this is just the right weight (5lbs) on average and the screen displays a clear wide field. The keyboard is designed as to not accumulate undesirable debris in and around the keys. To me this computer is beautiful. The camera display is a little gritty though, you may want a monitor display with a higher pixel number, but seeing internet information and document information is all great, clear, vivid colors and well defined. Even my Zoom meetings the picture comes out clear and well defined, it's just the fuzziness when you click on the camera.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 16, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Turn-On Switch Problem; Horrible Screen Resolution
reviews.reviewText: This Laptop has an SSD drive and sometimes will not boot-up for periods of up to 15-20 min or more after pressing the on switch. Screen problems are horrific. Often can barely see writing, spaces and symbols with moving PC around for better angle.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great value...great laptop!
reviews.reviewText: Just started using my new HP laptop and I love it! After trying different brands in the past, and doing a bit of research, I chose this one. Large screen, great quality, good price. Exactly what I needed!
